{"_id":"PwzyJrlKprqNeJIz","name":"Macros for SWADE","content":"<h1>Macros for SWADE</h1>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/sundries/gaming/playing-cards.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Chase</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Run the macro.</li>\n<li>You can select a Deck. You can set to dogfight.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Rules</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.nB1vsvPTn5jSRG6v]{Chases and Vehicles}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/weapons/thrown/dynamite-simple-brown.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Deviation</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Run the macro and it will tell will where to land the template.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Rules</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.xxEcWExtn36PPxg0]{Area Effect Attacks}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/creatures/mammals/wolf-shadow-black.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Gang Up</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Select one token.</li>\n<li>Target another token.</li>\n<li>Run the macro. It'll calculate the Ganging Up bonus. </li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Important</p>\n<p>This macro uses token disposition to indentify friend from foe. Be sure to set them property.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Module</p>\n<p>Token Faction is recommended.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Rules</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.hdXOHCe38O8KGyUz]{Ganging Up}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/commodities/biological/tentacle-purple-white.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Grappling</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Select one token.</li>\n<li>Target another token.</li>\n<li>Run the macro. It'll calculate the Ganging Up bonus + Size/Scale bonus. </li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Important</p>\n<p>This macro uses token disposition to indentify friend from foe. Be sure to set them property.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Module</p>\n<p>Token Faction is recommended.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Rules</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.od3tHNJTS8Ma4n2o]{Grappling}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/environment/people/charge.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Mass Battle</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Run the macro.</li>\n<li>Fill the data.</li>\n<li>Battle!</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Rules</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.IJkWxV4kddDaU0Gl]{Mass Battles}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/magic/time/arrows-circling-pink.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Next Turn</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>It'll skip the current turn if are in combat.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/magic/time/clock-stopwatch-white-blue.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Quick Combat</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Run the macro.</li>\n<li>It'll select ALL tokens in the active scene, send them to combat tracker and draw the cards.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/magic/control/fear-fright-white.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Unshaken</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Select a token.</li>\n<li>Run the macro.</li>\n<li>If the token is shaken it will offer to roll spirit and spend a benny on failure.</li>\n<li>If the token is unshaken it will set the Shaken status to it.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Rules</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.30TJKevSbgxK6jQy]{Damage Effects}</p>\n<p> </p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"tckKxzbezKvre3KI":3},"flags":{}}
